---
description: When editing Markdown. Apply for .md files so lint stays clean.
globs: "**/*.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Markdown

- **Config**: [.markdownlint.yaml](.markdownlint.yaml). Respect it so pre-commit and editor agree.
- **Section titles**: Use real headings (`##`, `###`), not standalone bold/italic (avoids MD036).
- **Duplicate headings**: Same heading text under different parent sections is allowed (MD024 siblings_only). Avoid duplicate heading text within the same section.
- **Tables**: Simple tables are fine; alignment is not required (MD060 disabled).
